{"tid":1904193,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【新冠肺炎】英超倘腰斬如何處理？　英媒：利物浦或失冠軍","createTime":"2020-02-29T12:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T14:19:39.000Z","uid":193217,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44812d589c4fad5ec7d23093038a15164461b01f","tid":1904193,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"新型肺炎（俗稱武漢肺炎）在全球肆虐，在歐洲不斷擴散下，多項大型體育賽事受影響，如意甲需延期或閉門作賽。<br />\n<br />\n英國亦不斷有新增確診個案下，英超亦有機會遭波及。有英國傳媒指，英超倘腰斬，利物浦或失去本應手到拿來的聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n英國《Daily Telegraph》指出，若英超因疫情而遭政府下令腰斬、而球季餘下賽事無法進行的話，賽例本身並無明文會如何處理這種情況。換言之，倘賽事取消，利物浦即使在榜首遙遙領先，亦未必可獲球會史上首個英超冠軍、亦是苦候30年的頂級聯賽冠軍。但對榜尾球隊來說就不一樣，若然賽事腰斬，正在降班區的3支球隊亦未必需要降班。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係空場踢睇最後10場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa97dc535d5f60bd05ed5d4e2be6959590ced7f","tid":1904193,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6709acf5fd248c975bfd44740c9f3e8b3f623c69","tid":1904193,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得意甲果邊斬既可能性非常大<br />\n最終無一隊冠軍<br />\n英超好少會去到空場."},{"pid":"330195c820b79cba5fc349c433bd97d9fb722b9f","tid":1904193,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"支持呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfae29ec357ba4a13d3906526163b3ea2fc888a","tid":1904193,"uid":15830,"like":0,"d